非常对 现实就是如此 只是说出来普罗大众的玻璃心接受不了」。百度副总裁璩静谈管人引争议：员工闹分手提离职我秒批！为什么要考虑员工的家庭！网友：人不是冷冰冰的机器"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-60b1a971155795004a1ec2df37a4948b_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "188 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655203171"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhZv2/IqSz+lYEAMaCTEwNzg3ODI3OSCG7OWxBjAAOOUIQANyCTY1NTIwMzE3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1715116582.600606", "card_id": "Q_655221347", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 371}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中法发布关于中东局势的联合声明，呼吁各方在奥运会期间休战，还有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e5678b6b626206600889de4047caa6f7_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "149 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655221347"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhZv2/IqSz+lYEAMaCTEwNzg4MjI4MyDX2+axBjAAOIAJQARyCTY1NTIyMTM0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1715116582.601026", "card_id": "Q_651246802", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 508}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么大家对雷军的评价这么高？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "从个人经历上讲四位都是传奇，从战略角度上讲任马是领先的，从利民角度上讲四位相差也不大（只说小马的即时通讯不讲游戏），从利国的角度讲任正非是遥遥领先的， 我真的搞不懂为什么雷军在民间评价这么高，在我眼里这四位都没有背叛自己的阶级，都是很刻板印象的企业家，为啥大家对雷军就评价这么好这么高？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d4c95c4a32a80899c6e645dbd4df3ff_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "144 万热度", "font_color": "", "backgro